item.title: Desktop Elements Detection Using Deep Learning
item.description: Notes The original post (written with Joseph Paillard) has been published on the Amossys blog. Here, some elements related to the Amossys company (and not paramount on this blog) have been removed. Prediction sample Context This project has been carried out as part of the AI & Cyber challenge that took place during the European Cyber Week (ECW) 2020. This year, the challenge was to emulate human behavior on a computer.
